trans-unit.source: Represents a single item of data extracted from a workflow and all its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: 表示从工作流以及所有关联的批注中提取数据的单个项。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a track point, it sends a tracking record to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]当运行时跟踪基础结构匹配了跟踪点时，它会将跟踪记录发送到跟踪服务。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> may contain <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects that specify data to be extracted from the workflow and returned in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> or the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>或者<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>可能包含<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>或<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>对象，指定要从流中提取数据并在<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>或<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>中返回</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: A TrackingDataItem represents a single item of this extracted data in either <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: TrackingDataItem 表示在其中一种<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>或<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>此提取数据的单个项

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> class.
Gets and sets the list of annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: 获取和设置与提取的数据关联的批注的列表。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> can specify annotations to be sent with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>或<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>可以指定要与提取的数据一起发送的批注。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: These are contained in the Annotations property.
trans-unit.target: 这些批注包含在批注属性。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> ，其中包含与提取的数据关联的批注。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the extracted data associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置与关联的提取的数据<xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Data contains the member data, specified by an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, that was extracted from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: 数据包含指定的成员数据<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>或<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>，工作流实例中提取。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that represents the extracted data.
Gets or sets the name of the property or field associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置与提取的数据关联的字段的属性的名称。

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure supports data extraction on fields and properties of classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; a member of such a field or property; and a single item of a field or a property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface, for example a single element in a collection.
trans-unit.target: 运行时跟踪基础结构上继承的类的字段和属性支持数据提取<xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; 此类字段或属性; 的成员以及单个项的字段或属性 （或其中任何的成员） 实现<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>接口，例如集合中的单一元素。</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: FieldName contains the dot delineated name of the item extracted and is equivalent to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> depending on which type of extract specified the data contained by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.
trans-unit.target: FieldName 包含点分隔的提取项目名称，并且等效于<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>或<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>具体取决于哪种提取指定的数据包含受支持<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>

trans-unit.source: The dot delineated name of the property or field that was extracted.
trans-unit.target: 用点分隔的属性或提取的字段的名称。
